      72.02,
      550.08,
      543.41,
      567.61
    ],
    "text": "The Petitioner states that on 3.2.2012, the 3rd Respondent who is the Medical",
    "fonts": [
      "Times New Roman"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      9.0,
      14.039999961853027
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 1,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      576.19,
      543.55,
      591.73
    ],
    "text": "Officer-in-Charge of the said hospital called the Petitioner to staff rest room; that",
    "fonts": [
      "Times New Roman"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      14.039999961853027
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 1,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      598.44,
      543.13,
      615.97
    ],
    "text": "the 3rd Respondent questioned the Petitioner about the poisoning of the Water tank",
    "fonts": [
      "Times New Roman"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      9.0,
      14.039999961853027
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 1,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      622.56,
      543.46,
      640.09
    ],
