    "fonts": [
      "Times New Roman"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      9.0,
      14.039999961853027
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 1,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      648.67,
      543.6,
      664.21
    ],
    "text": "with a rubber pipe. The Petitioner sustained injuries. The Judicial Medical officer",
    "fonts": [
      "Times New Roman"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      14.039999961853027
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 1,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      672.79,
      543.02,
      688.33
    ],
    "text": "(JMO) who examined the Petitioner on 4.12.2012 observed five contusions on the",
