      "Times New Roman"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      14.039999961853027
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 1,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      697.05,
      543.21,
      712.59
    ],
    "text": "right upper arm, back of the chest and right buttock of the Petitioner. The JMO in",
